data.description: Welcome to this Stunning ranch style home in the desirable Deer Creek Farm boasting a large, finished walk-out basement on 1.56 acres at the end of a cul-de-sac with gorgeous mountain views!  This inviting home has an open concept floor plan with extensive rich hardwood floors, vaulted ceilings and newer interior paint and updates.  For culinary enthusiasts, the newly renovated kitchen is a dream come true. Featuring a large center island, Quartz countertops, 42-inch shaker-style cabinets, a farm-style stainless steel sink, and a 48-inch Thermador 6-burner gas stove with a custom stainless steel hood vent, it's a chef's haven. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the spacious dining room and family room, where a floor-to-ceiling stone gas fireplace adds warmth and charm, complemented by mountain views. The main floor is thoughtfully designed, featuring a convenient office with French doors, a generous laundry room with a utility sink, a bedroom with a dual door and private bath, and a primary bedroom with a double-sided fireplace, expansive ensuite including a large soaking tub, granite countertops with dual sinks, a spacious shower with frameless glass, and a walk-in closet. The finished walkout basement transforms into an entertainment area and an ideal place for relaxing. A vast media room with a 120-inch screen and projector, a built-in wet bar with granite, cabinets, and a mini-fridge, and a large game room area which opens up to an expanded stamped patio. This outdoor space is equipped with a new gas line for a fire pit or grill and a hot tub, creating an ideal setting for gatherings.  Further enhancing the home's appeal is a brand-new roof and gutters, new exterior paint in 2022, metal storm shields over every window, two commercial hot water heaters, and a water softener. This residence effortlessly combines style, functionality, and modern amenities for an unparalleled living experience.
